<DATE>03/28/2008</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Jim</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>Great riding and driving truck! Can handle the occassional work load well! Good reliabilty! The new six speed automatic transmission is a dissappointment! I currently still own a 2500hd classic with the old 4 speed automatic trans and under similar driving conditions cosistently gets 3.1 miles per gallon better fuel economy! I would have expected the 6 speed to get better fuel economy than the old one! </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Great Interior design and comfort! </FAVORITE>
